nodes.text: During the height of the Galactic Civil War, shortly after the Battle of Yavin, there were a series of H-shaped Space Stations that were in use by both the Galactic Empire and the Rebel Alliance, as well as for civilian purposes. One of these was the Dantooine Space Station, with others including the Yavin 4 Station, the Tatooine Space Station, the Lok Station, the Deep Space Station bordering Kessel and Deep Space, the Naboo Space Station, and others.
A toy model version of the Space Stations was also supplied during Empire Day, by both the Galactic Empire and the Rebel Alliance (the latter via Remembrance Day).
